N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 7101.2 - Definition

State Regulations

Records shall mean only those written
documents relating to the nomination process which may, pursuant to section
66
of the

Judiciary Law, be made public. Such records shall include the reports issued by
the commission to the Governor of nominations made by the commission, press
releases issued by the commission and such other documents as the commission
has made publicly available in the course of its functions. Notes
